  ('optometrist-moex-00414', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '硬式隱形眼鏡（Rigidcontactlens）的配戴，可藉由中和（neutralize）下列那個部位的光線折射，以降低眼 睛的球面像差（ocularsphericalaberration）？', '["角膜基質層", "角膜前表面", "角膜後表面", "水晶體"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00415', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關鏡片色像差（chromaticaberration）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["分為軸性（axial或longitudinal）和橫向性（transverse或lateral）兩類", "成因是不同顏色的光，其波長不同", "軸性色像差與稜鏡效應（prismaticeffect）有關", "冠冕玻璃（crownglass）的阿貝數比polycarbonate鏡片高"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00416', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於折射的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["光線由光密介質進入光疏介質，折射光會偏離法線", "不同波長的光在介質中傳播時速度不同", "在介質中，波長越短所對應的折射率越小", "光線由光密介質進入光疏介質時，在交界面可能產生全反射"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00417', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關色散（dispersion）基本概念之敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["正常人眼可感知的可見光波長介於380~780nm", "色像差（chromaticaberration）之產生，是由於眼內光學介質的折射率會隨著可見光波長增加而增加", "較短波長之藍光會較紅光來得更容易折射", "不同波長可見光的相對亮度（Relativeluminosity）可以“V（λ）Function”來表示"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00418', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '空氣中一片薄透鏡，折射率為1.5，屈光度為+3.00DS。已知前凸表面曲率半徑為10公分，則此透鏡側面 形狀和後表面曲率半徑為何？', '["新月形，20公分", "雙凸形，20公分", "新月形，25公分", "雙凸形，50公分"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
