  ('optometrist-moex-00420', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列為光在介質中的行進速度，何者之折射率最大？', '["150,000公里/秒", "176,470公里/秒", "179,640公里/秒", "187,500公里/秒"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00421', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '若一光線從冕牌玻璃（n=1.52）射入空氣中，在空氣中的折射光線與法線的夾角為30.00 ，則入射光與法 線的夾角為何？ °', '["16.14", "39.96", "19.20", "49.46"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
